When you try to add the class (at the very beginning), are you checking the "waitlist if class is full" button?

If you forgot to click the waitlist if class is full option, follow these instructions from SIS:

From your shopping cart, click the hyperlink for the class. This will take you back to the Class Preferences page where you can select the ‘Wait list if class is full’ box. Proceed back to your shopping cart and finish enrolling as usual.

When you try to add the class (at the very beginning), are you checking the "waitlist if class is full" button?

Please contact Lydia Raya, lraya@eecs.
